     │ and no project_id, so the AI literally cannot be "project‑aware." The pill knows the projectId; the request                                                                     │
     │ never sends it. An auth + projectId → chat bridge is the missing spine of the always‑prepared AI, and it                                                                        │
     │ is in none of the piece docs. Until it exists, every P2 prompt is theater.                                                                                                      │
