     │ The spine that makes four journeys feel like one product                                                                                                                        │
     │                                                                                                                                                                                 │
     │ 1. One persistent AI, two contexts. Outside mode (whole site, saves work) ↔ Project mode (all‑project‑aware,                                                                    │
     │ current‑project focused), joined by project_id + the context bus — not two bots. Already mounted in the                                                                         │
     │ root layout; do not add key={pathname} above it (would unmount on every switch and kill the premise).                                                                           │
     │ 2. The context bus = ONE channel. In‑session half = setAiContext (P1). Durable half = project_feed (P3).                                                                        │
     │ Every surface emits; P2's prompt engine reads both + the digest. No ad‑hoc AI wiring.                                                                                           │
     │ 3. Convergence is cheap‑work‑upstream. REAL tier (deterministic, ~free): summaries, chartable‑combo detection,                                                                  │
     │ recipe pre‑resolution, cross‑project identity index. SELECTIVE (one LLM pass on a strong signal): pre‑build                                                                     │
     │ one sample deliverable. REACH (reframe): never pre‑build every option. Projects feels instant because the                                                                       │
     │ cheap work already happened.                                                                                                                                                    │
     │ 4. Always shippable. Every wave below leaves the cockpit working — the broker never lands on a half‑built page.                                                                 │
